Author: Rhyanon
Text: Honestly after some sleep I'm doing better. In any case, honestly thank-you. I'm really sorry to hear that you had a bad day too and I hope today is being kinder to you.   I might try and recover idk im sick of my life revolving around this shit

Author: boo_snug
Text: I don’t know what to say except I am thinking of you. I too had a rough day, tried to restrict, failed at restricting, so I ended up binging. Or at least in my head I consider it binging. It’s hard. And frustrating. And I hate myself for it.  Anyways you aren’t alone and you can do this.
